   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1660_dai_lns235ms_l1_r.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>الله اکبر</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
            <p>God is great</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبده الاماثل و الاقران    
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم</persName>
               چودری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
               قانونوگوی
               <lb/>پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               را انهاء انکه درینولا مشیخت پناه محبان اعتضادی خلیفه جیو
               <lb/>ظاهر کردند که یکنفر شتر ایشان از قصبه
               <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName>
               بدزدی رفته است
               <lb/>لهذا نگاشته می آید که سراغ آنرا بگیرید  و چنان سعی و
               <lb/>تلاش درینماده بکار برید که شتر مذکور پیدا شود
               <lb/>یقین که درین باب خود را معاف نخواهد دانست و
               <lb/>قدغن بلیغ خواهند نمود تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>۲۷</num>
               محرم سنه
              <num>۱۰۷۱</num>
              </date>               
              <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            </p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>Eminent among Equals and Contemporaries <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam [Das]</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref>
               <lb/>of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, [be] informed that at this time the Venerable Refuge of Friends in Need <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_khalifa">Khalifa</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>
               <lb/>has declared that one of his camels has been stolen from the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba</ref> of <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName>.
               <lb/>Therefore it is noted that a search should be made, and likewise make such efforts and
               <lb/>inquiries in this matter that the said camel shall be found.
               <lb/>It is certain that in this matter, [<persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>] should not consider themselves excused,
               and
               <lb/>great care should be taken. Written on the <date calendar="#hijri-qamri"><num>27th</num> of Muharram in the year
               1071</date>.
               <g ref="#faqat">Nothing further</g>.
            </p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>ھو</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>

         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p>
               <lb/>حسب المسطور مقرر شناسند
               <lb/>نهایت تاکید دانند انچه نگارد
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
               <lb/><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                  <persName ref="#asadullah">اسد الله</persName>
                  مرید
                  <unclear>اخلاص</unclear>
                  <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازش خانی</persName>
                  </mentioned></stamp></p>
         </div>   
               
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p>
               <lb/>Understand it to be settled as written
               <lb/>and enjoined completely, and so it should be written. <g ref="#baiz">Ended</g>.
               <lb/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#asadullah">Asadullah</persName>, <unclear>sincere</unclear> disciple of <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName></mentioned></stamp><note>This seal, which probably belonged to Asadullah, a deputy of the noble Nawazish Khan, also appears in the document titled <ref type="document" target="#lf_pDas_1659_dai_lns235ms_q1">Order of Asadullah to Purshottam Das and Paras Ram regarding removal of soldiers from villages</ref>.</note>
            </p>
         </div>

         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1660_dai_lns235ms_l1_v.jpg"/>

         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p>
               پروانه وکالت
               <app><rdg cert="high">دستگاه بنابر</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="low">پرگنه
                  <placeName ref="#dhar">دهار</placeName></rdg></app>
               <lb rend="empty"/>شتر خلیفه جیو
            </p>
         </div>

         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p>
                a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">parvana</ref> 
               <app><rdg cert="high">of the Deputy of Excellence, regarding</rdg>
                  <rdg cert="low">in the charge of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#dhar">Dhar</placeName></rdg></app>
               <lb rend="empty"/>a camel of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_khalifa">Khalifa</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Jiu</ref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
